{"tid":1050974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"交易平台創辦人猝逝　值10億元虛擬貨幣遭鎖死","createTime":"2019-03-07T08:40:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T07:00:11.000Z","uid":130626,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"028fd92938b86614711e799c39ecf3a9efa21b26","tid":1050974,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T08:40:24.000Z","msg":"加拿大加密虛擬貨幣交易平台Quadriga創辦人科滕（Gerald Cotten）去年12月猝死，由於他是唯一掌有存取權限密碼的人，平台上客戶儲存約值1.8億加幣（約10.7億港元）的虛擬貨幣被「鎖死」。有客戶威脅告上法庭，Quadriga上周向法院申請債權人保護，法官周二（5日）裁定，給Quadriga30天時間解決。<br />\n成立了5年的Quadriga平台，涉及的虛擬貨幣包括比特幣（Bitcoin）、萊特幣（Litecoin）和以太幣（Ethereum）。Quadriga上月14日在facebook的貼文說，年僅30歲的創辦人科滕（Gerald Cotten），在印度孤兒院當義工期間病逝。<br />\n科滕的遺孀羅伯遜（Jennifer Robertson）代表公司提交的書面證辭稱，Quadriga註冊用戶達36.3萬人，現時共欠11.5萬名用戶總值2.5億加幣（14.9億港元）的虛擬幣，當中很多都儲存在科滕主電腦中的虛擬貨幣「冷錢包」（cold wallet）。虛擬貨幣投資者為防黑客入侵，不少將錢包存放在未有上網的電子產品。<br />\n羅伯遜稱並未參與丈夫業務，對密碼或恢復鑰匙一無所知。她又在書面證詞稱指，不斷收到網上威脅和「誹謗評論」，質疑科滕死因的真相，甚至他是否真的死了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190206/s00005/9ee2bbb6e4985250d2a7757e5e3b6185.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190206%2Fs00005%2F9ee2bbb6e4985250d2a7757e5e3b6185.jpg&h=e9a8c43e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20190206/s00005/1549461345491/%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%E5%89%B5%E8%BE%A6%E4%BA%BA%E7%8C%9D%E9%80%9D-%E5%80%BC10%E5%84%84%E5%85%83%E8%99%9B%E6%93%AC%E8%B2%A8%E5%B9%A3%E9%81%AD%E9%8E%96%E6%AD%BB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20190206%2Fs00005%2F1549461345491%2F%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%2598%2593%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%258F%25B0%25E5%2589%25B5%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%258C%259D%25E9%2580%259D-%25E5%2580%25BC10%25E5%2584%2584%25E5%2585%2583%25E8%2599%259B%25E6%2593%25AC%25E8%25B2%25A8%25E5%25B9%25A3%25E9%2581%25AD%25E9%258E%2596%25E6%25AD%25BB&d=m7n5JD7ZMd19sx07z0x1QEzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=9b796952\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20190206%2Fs00005%2F1549461345491%2F%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%2598%2593%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%258F%25B0%25E5%2589%25B5%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%258C%259D%25E9%2580%259D-%25E5%2580%25BC10%25E5%2584%2584%25E5%2585%2583%25E8%2599%259B%25E6%2593%25AC%25E8%25B2%25A8%25E5%25B9%25A3%25E9%2581%25AD%25E9%258E%2596%25E6%25AD%25BB&h=ccb46005\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20190206/s00005/1549461345491/%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%E5%89%B5%E8%BE%A6%E4%BA%BA%E7%8C%9D%E9%80%9D-%E5%80%BC10%E5%84%84%E5%85%83%E8%99%9B%E6%93%AC%E8%B2%A8%E5%B9%A3%E9%81%AD%E9%8E%96%E6%AD%BB</a>"},{"pid":"42dc7ebac72a18cc311be0763df9970c3b0fd38c","tid":1050974,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T09:00:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n贏"},{"pid":"0aec9a490694d041308e01d2eb8ad8bc8a8980c3","tid":1050974,"uid":55597,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T09:43:36.000Z","msg":"呢件事都算係一個警號"},{"pid":"b73d6c89420addeafcc68d5c7113766bf31085b3","tid":1050974,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T10:34:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"527a13071a987034f76d0b91b0aa6039dee56924","tid":1050974,"uid":19725,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T10:48:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係印度買左個島做皇帝了<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"404a381c3bb55527a7a7a4d1b202e79bb5c70eac","tid":1050974,"uid":152104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T12:31:57.000Z","msg":"ready  player 1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3056c83c720bc616c15e253a1f346c27bc4ef43d","tid":1050974,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim